§2/neoforge generate start <x> <y> <z> <kamakaRaadius> [progressiRiba] §r§f- Genereerib antud positsiooni keskpunktis oleva ruudu, mille mõlemad küljed on kamakaRaadius * 2.
§2/neoforge generate stop §r§f- Peatab käimasoleva genereerimise ja kuvab lõpule viidud progressi.
§2/neoforge generate status §r- Kuvab hetkel käimasoleva genereerimise progressi.
§2/neoforge generate help §r- Kuvab seda sõnumit
Üldine nõuanne: Serverikonsoolis sisestades saad genereerimist käivitada erinevates dimensioonides, kasutades /execute in <dimensioon> neoforge generate...

neoforge.configuration.uitext.title: %s Configuration

neoforge.configuration.uitext.notonline.text: Settings in here are determined by the server and cannot be changed while online.

neoforge.configuration.uitext.notlan.text: Settings in here cannot be edited while your game is open to LAN. Please return to the main menu and load the world again.

neoforge.configuration.uitext.notloaded.text: Settings in here are only available while a world is loaded.

neoforge.configuration.uitext.unsupporte.text: This value cannot be edited in the UI. Please contact the mod author about providing a custom UI for it.

neoforge.configuration.uitext.longstring.text: This value is too long to be edited in the UI. Please edit it in the config file.

neoforge.configuration.uitext.undo.toolt: Reverts changes on this screen only.
neoforge.configuration.uitext.reset.tool: Reverts everything on this screen to its default value.
neoforge.configuration.uitext.restart.ga: One or more of the configuration option that were changed will only take effect when the game is started.
neoforge.configuration.uitext.restart.se: One or more of the configuration option that were changed will only take effect when the world is reloaded.

neoforge.configuration.uitext.restart.re.text: Your changes will have no effect until you restart!

neoforge.configuration.title: NeoForge Configuration
neoforge.configgui.advertiseDedicatedSer: Set this to true to enable advertising the dedicated server to local LAN clients so that it shows up in the Multiplayer screen automatically.
neoforge.configgui.forgeLightPipelineEna: Luba Forge'i plokirenderduse ootejärjekord - parandab kohandatud mudelite valgustust.
neoforge.configgui.fullBoundingBoxLadder: Sea see väärtuseks "true", et kontrollida redelite puhul olemi terve piirdekasti läbistavust, selle asemel, et kontrollida ainult, mis plokis nad on. Põhjustab nähtavaid erinevusi mehaanikas, seega vaikeväärtus on vanilli käitumine. Vaikimisi: "false".
A config option mainly for developers. Logs out modded tags that are using the 'forge' namespace when running on integrated server. Defaults to DEV_SHORT.
neoforge.configgui.logUntranslatedConfig: A config option mainly for developers. Logs out configuration values that do not have translations when running a client in a development environment.
neoforge.configgui.logUntranslatedItemTa: A config option mainly for developers. Logs out modded item tags that do not have translations when running on integrated server. Format desired is tag.item.<namespace>.<path> for the translation key. Defaults to SILENCED.
neoforge.configgui.permissionHandler.too: The permission handler used by the server. Defaults to neoforge:default_handler if no such handler with that name is registered.
neoforge.configgui.removeErroringBlockEn: Set this to true to remove any Entity that throws an error in its update method instead of closing the server and reporting a crash log.

neoforge.configgui.removeErroringBlockEn.text:
BE WARNED THIS COULD SCREW UP EVERYTHING.
USE SPARINGLY.
WE ARE NOT RESPONSIBLE FOR DAMAGES.

neoforge.configgui.removeErroringEntitie: Set this to true to remove any BlockEntity that throws an error in its update method instead of closing the server and reporting a crash log.

neoforge.configgui.removeErroringEntitie.text:
BE WARNED THIS COULD SCREW UP EVERYTHING.
USE SPARINGLY.
WE ARE NOT RESPONSIBLE FOR DAMAGES.

neoforge.configgui.showLoadWarnings.tool: Lubamisel kuvab NeoForge mistahes hoiatusi, mis esinesid laadimise käigus.
neoforge.configgui.useCombinedDepthStenc: Set to true to use a combined DEPTH_STENCIL attachment instead of two separate ones.
